  <description><![CDATA[<p>In an idyllic location, directly on the shores of Lake Thun the Bellevue au Lac is an attractive hotel with good facilities and light, spacious rooms. In the heart of this lakeside village, guests here will enjoy a relaxing stay with easy access to historic Thun and the surrounding area from the boat stop just 2 minutes’ walk away (200m). The local bus, free with your guest card, also stops just 50m away.</p>]]></description>
